div.div:
Notes
1- if there's no avatar_image then we will provide a default one
2- price must be stored in database in cents and shown in dollars
3- in gym page created at must be shown as date only
4- before deleting a gym make sure it dosn't have a training sessions
5- one gym has many gym managers
6- in training sessions starts_at, finishes_at => dataTime
7- before editing or deleting a training_session make sure there are no users - attended that session
8- when editing session we can edit date & time only if there's no user attended the session
9- when creating a new training session make sure it dosn't overlap with any other training session in that gym.10 - when the admin changes package price or package sessions number it won't affect on bought packages.
11- any training package must be bought from a gym, so iif the admin is going to buy a package for a user he must choose a gym from drop_down list, and the same will be for city manager.
